title: Acaya Open
text: The Acaya Open was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Challenge%20Tour">Challenge Tour</a>, played at the Acaya Golf Resort in <a href="Italy">Italy</a>. It was first held in 2011, when <a href="Jamie%20Moul">Jamie Moul</a> won the tournament. <a href="Espen%20Kofstad">Espen Kofstad</a> of Norway won the second and final event in 2012.
